CustomField.description:
The sum of the total number of children allowed for all indoor approved primary space rooms where “Will children in this room be over or under 2 1/2?” is marked Under or Both.
Value is determined based on room dimensions for rooms marked as serving children under 2 1/2 on the Classroom overlay(s) on the Room Information tab screen.
System displays whole number only, rounded down
CustomField.label: Max Under 2.5 Capacity
